<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-06-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-06-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="161" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d161">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">340.1115A/882a: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Chargé in Germany</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Heath</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-06-12">June 12,
                                    1940</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>1590. Please repeat following to Legations, Stockholm, Oslo,
                                Copenhagen, The Hague and Brussels.</p>
                            <p>Americans in Europe have been continually warned from the outbreak of
                                hostilities to depart for the United States while they could obtain
                                transportation. Practically all means of transportation to the
                                United States for them have now been cut off by Italy’s entry into
                                the war. The Department therefore will not further authorize loans
                                from its limited funds for repatriation expenses pending further
                                developments.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>